After touring most of the facility Inferno returned to Hydras with 
Waspinator in hand.
"Royalty.  I have found one of our colony's soldiers."  He said 
holding Waspinator up by the back of his wings.
"Eep!"  Waspinator covered his face with his hands as if that would 
stop him from being seen.
